'''阿格斯含硫原油价格指数'''（Argus Sour Crude Index）簡稱'''ASCI'''，是訂定長期[[原油|原油]]合約時的定價工具。

ASCI指數<ref name="Argus Sour Crude Index - Methodology and specificati ons guide">[http://www.argusmedia.com/ArgusStaticContent//Meth/ASCI.pdf Argus Sour Crude Index - Methodology and specifications guide]{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>是一個單日計算，以體積加權的平均油價，考慮三種不同等級的原油，不過將其視為是同一等級的原油處理。

三種原油分別是Mars、Poseidon及Southern Green Canyon。

由{{le|阿格斯媒體|Argus Media Ltd}}每天提供的ASCI可以表示美國[[墨西哥灣|墨西哥灣]]沿岸中級含硫原油的價格。

== 市場接受程度 ==
許多石油公司或產油國已接受用ASCI作為其原油價格的標準，如[[沙烏地阿拉伯國家石油公司|沙烏地阿拉伯國家石油公司]]（2009年）<ref name="Bloomberg - Saudi Aramco to Use Sour Oil Index as U.S. Benchmark - Drop WTI">Bloomberg - Saudi Aramco to Use Sour Oil Index as U.S. Benchmark, Drop WTI,[http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601207&sid=aW7G18EvCGD8] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601207&sid=aW7G18EvCGD8 |date=20190713132700 }}</ref>、科威特（2009年）<ref name="Reuters - Kuwait to price U.S. oil cargoes on ASCI">{{Cite web |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKN1418816120091214 |title=Reuters - Kuwait to price U.S. oil cargoes on ASCI |accessdate=2015-07-19 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713132702/https://uk.reuters.com/article/kuwait-oil-argus/update-1-kuwait-to-price-u-s-oil-cargoes-on-ascisources-idUKN1418816120091214 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及伊拉克（2010年）<ref name="Bloomberg - Iraq Will Use Argus Crude Price Formula From April">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601207&sid=aXffmkyVIbAU |title=Bloomberg - Iraq Will Use Argus Crude Price Formula From April |accessdate=2015-07-19 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713132701/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=e5621a50-a571-11e9-a8e0-3b33c46c9393&url=L2FwcHMvbmV3cz9waWQ9MjA2MDEyMDcmc2lkPWFYZmZta3lWSWJBVQ== |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Reuters - Iraq to switch to ASCI from U.S. crude futures">{{Cite web |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKLDE61A2TG20100211 |title=Reuters - Iraq to switch to ASCI from U.S. crude futures |accessdate=2015-07-19 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713132701/https://uk.reuters.com/article/markets-mediterranean-crude/med-crude-urals-lower-iraq-to-switch-benchmarks-idUKLDE61A2TG20100211 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

